### Variables
@baseURL = http://localhost:4000
@authToken ={{$dotenv TEST_AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Registrar dispositivo FCM - Caso exitoso
POST {{baseURL}}/devices/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "fcmToken": "dGhpcyBpcyBhIGZha2UgZmNtIHRva2VuIGZvciBleGFtcGxl"
}

### Registrar dispositivo FCM - Token largo (caso real)
POST {{baseURL}}/devices/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "fcmToken": "fGcM_token_example_1234567890abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ1234567890abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz"
}

### Registrar dispositivo FCM - Token vacío (debería fallar)
POST {{baseURL}}/devices/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "fcmToken": ""
}

### Registrar dispositivo FCM - Sin token (debería fallar)
POST {{baseURL}}/devices/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
}

### Registrar dispositivo FCM - Sin autenticación (debería fallar con 401)
POST {{baseURL}}/devices/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fcmToken": "dGhpcyBpcyBhIGZha2UgZmNtIHRva2VuIGZvciBleGFtcGxl"
}

### Registrar dispositivo FCM - Token inválido de autenticación (debería fallar con 401)
POST {{baseURL}}/devices/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here

{
  "fcmToken": "dGhpcyBpcyBhIGZha2UgZmNtIHRva2VuIGZvciBleGFtcGxl"
}